{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 45247933, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "PAN-EU-E-1", "title": "Capacity building actions", "publicationDateLong": 1654560000000, "callIdentifier": "EP-COMM-SUBV-2022-PAN-EU-E", "callTitle": "Pan-European Engagement Grant", "callccm2Id": 45080841, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43697167, "abbreviation": "EP", "description": "European Parliament"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 43697187, "abbreviation": "EP-1-1", "description": "Grants in the Area of Communication"}], "topicMGAs": [], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43694065, "abbreviation": "EP-AG", "description": "EP Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "22 June 2022", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["27 September 2022"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3413729": [{"action": "PAN-EU-E-2 - EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "22 June 2022", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["27 September 2022"], "budgetYearMap": {"2022": 2100000, "2023": 900000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "PAN-EU-E-1 - EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "22 June 2022", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["27 September 2022"], "budgetYearMap": {"2022": 2100000, "2023": 900000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "PAN-EU-E-3 - EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "22 June 2022", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["27 September 2022"], "budgetYearMap": {"2022": 2100000, "2023": 900000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2022", "2023"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">ExpectedOutcome</SPAN>:<p>The expected outcome of the actions financed under this call are:</p><ul level=\"0\"><li>An increased engagement of European citizens from as diverse public as possible with the construction of a vibrant European democracy, thus encouraging their active involvement as change-makers in the European Elections 2024 communication campaign.</li><li>An increased awareness among European citizens from as diverse public as possible about the actions of the European Union and its institutions, in particular the European Parliament;</li><li>The establishment of pan-European participatory channels, connecting the European Parliament with its citizens and encouraging their active participation in together.eu, the platform of the European Parliament</li> </ul>\n<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Objective</SPAN>:<p>The European Parliament is looking to co-finance projects articulating a coherent, consistent and cost efficient work programme to encourage and support citizens, who volunteer to become elections change-makers by organising capacity building actions offline and online,</p>\n<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p>This action consists of the design and implementation of capacity building through training and other actions, aiming at providing change-makers with skills, competences, tools and motivation to play an active role in the democratic life and in the promotion of the democratic values, especially by mobilising their community to participate in the European Elections in 2024.</p><p>After the training, the beneficiary should monitor and report on the communication engagement activities organised by the trained change-makers. The change-makers should commit to organise at least 2 activities with an outreach of at least 100 persons in total in a physical setting in their community using the skills and competences previously acquired through capacity-building.</p>\n", "conditions": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#404040;&#10;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Conditions</span></b><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#404040;&#10;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#404040;mso-themecolor:&#10;text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">1.&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Admissibility conditions: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in section 8 of the call document</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Proposal page limits and layout:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:&#10;EN-US\">&nbsp;described in the application form - Part B&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">and the</span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/om_en.pdf\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Online Manual</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:10.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;115%\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2. Eligible countries: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in section&nbsp;</span>9 of the call document</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. Other eligibility conditions:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> described in section 9 of the call document<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b>4. Financial and operational capacity and exclusion: </b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">described in </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">section 10 of the call document</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"FR-BE\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:FR-BE\">5.&nbsp;Evaluation and award:&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"FR-BE\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:FR-BE\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<ul>\r\n    <li>&nbsp;<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;&#10;     mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Submission and evaluation processes</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> described <span style=\"color:#404040;&#10;     mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191\">section 11 of the call document and      the</span> </span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/om_en.pdf\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Online Manual</span></a><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\n<ul>\r\n    <li>&nbsp;<b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Award criteria, scoring and      thresholds:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">      described in section 12 of the call document<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\n<p><span id=\"1617195973454S\" style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"1617195972667S\" style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Indicative timeline for      evaluation and grant agreement: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">described in      section 7 of the call document<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\n<p><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#404040;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-ansi-language:&#10;EN-US\">6</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">. Legal and financial set-up of the grants: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">described <span style=\"co